upsgi install/build notes

Quick local build
- CPUCOUNT=1 python3 upsgiconfig.py --build default
- ./upsgi --version

Alternative local build path when your environment already matches the default build profile closely
- make
- ./upsgi --version

Quick local validation
- prove -I tests/fork/lib tests/fork/regression/*.t tests/fork/fault/*.t
- tests/fork/soak/request_burst_smoke.sh
- tests/fork/soak/reload_cycle_smoke.sh

